metadata.name: ILLUMINATI
metadata.description: "The path to enlightenment is a perilous one, hidden in darkness and guarded by formidable powers. But for those who dare to journey forth, the reward is a view from the summit, where one can bask in the bright light of wisdom and insight, and wield power over all below. The path may be perilous, but for the genuinely perceptive and crafty, the prize of true enlightenment waits, gleaming like a beacon of hope and luring you forward with the promise of inexhaustible knowledge and dominance."
